      "title": "Lapping Polishing Grinding Machines Products Services",
      "description": "LAPMASTER WOLTERS provides industrial lapping machines, ultrasonic cleaners diamond powder and abrasive compounds for grinding and polishing equipment.",
      "text_excerpt": "Lapping Polishing Grinding Machines Products Services\nSawing, Lapping, Grinding & Polishing\nLeading solution provider for sophisticated solutions in high-precision flat finishing or lapping.\nPrecision Meets Innovation\nDiscover our advanced technology for perfect surface finishes.\nCuriosity, courage and innovative strength\nWhat sets us apart from others.\nMachines are high-performance tools. We make them what they are: Your companion on the road to success.\nCome join our team\nBecause people make the difference.\nWhether in sales, production, research & development, service or administration. It is always people who determine the international success of Lapmaster Wolters.\nLapping, Polishing, Grinding Machines and Services\nIn today's technologically advanced world, there are a growing number of applications where conventional machining techniques just aren't accurate enough to meet precision surfacing requirements. Precision surfacing with abrasive media, a technology developed and refined by LAPMASTER WOLTERS over the past 200 years, can often be the answer.\nHowever, it takes more than the technology alone to produce precision surfacing and honing specifications. It takes a company with extensive knowledge and experience with a broad range of materials and applications.  A company capable of creating customized, turnkey precision surfacing solutions utilizing the latest conventional and superabrasive grinding techniques...It takes LAPMASTER WOLTERS, your partner in precision surfacing technology. We offer\nLapping Machines\nPolishing Machines\nFine Grinding Machines\nSingle Wafer &\nSiC\nProcessing Machines\n, Brush Deburring Machines, Creep Feed Grinding Machines, Double Disc Grinding Machines, Buffing Machines in our ever growing product line.\nPrecision at a nano level\nKey competencies perfectly combined.\nOur passion for excellent manufacturing environments, complex supply chains, a highly specialized workforce and adherence to strict regulatory standards makes us the perfect supplier for semiconductor technologies.\nLearn More\nCuriosity, courage, and innovative spirit\nWhat sets us apart from others?\nMachines are high-performance tools. We make them what they are: Your partners on the road to success.\nPrevious\nNext"
